{
  "texts": [
    "The residuals of these models represent perceived personality traits cleaned of the influence of these variables.",
    "Next, we predict these residuals from public figures' names' embeddings using Ridge regression.",
    "The results presented in Fig. 1 (red bars) show that GPT-3 can accurately predict perceived personality even when controlling for demographics and likability.",
    "The accuracy decreased but remained very high, ranging from r = 0.53 for emotional stability to r = 0.70 for extraversion, which translates into Cohen's d range of d = 1.25 (very large effect) to d = 1.96 (very large effect).",
    "The raw (uncorrected) accuracies range from r = 0.43 to r = 0.61."
  ]
}